<!-- Methodology Section -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <h2 class="section-title">Methodology</h2>
    <div class="row">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Analytical Approach</h5>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Text Preprocessing:</strong> Cleaning, tokenization, stopword removal, and lemmatization to prepare text for analysis</li>
                        <li><strong>Sentiment Analysis:</strong> Using VADER to quantify the positive, negative, or neutral sentiment in each review</li>
                        <li><strong>Word Clouds:</strong> Visualization of frequently mentioned terms for different sentiment categories</li>
                        <li><strong>N-gram Analysis:</strong> Identifying common phrases and word pairs to understand context</li>
                        <li><strong>Topic modelling:</strong> Using Non-negative Matrix Factorization (NMF) to identify key themes in reviews</li>
                        <li><strong>Aspect-Based Sentiment Analysis:</strong> Extracting sentiment about specific product features</li>
                        <li><strong>Review Length Analysis:</strong> Examining the relationship between review length and sentiment/helpfulness</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Key Findings -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <h2 class="section-title">Key Findings</h2>
    
    <!-- Product Statistics and Sentiment -->
    <div class="card visualization-card mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">1. Product Ratings and Overall Sentiment</h4>
            <p class="card-text">Analysis of ratings and sentiment scores revealed significant differences in customer satisfaction across products. While ratings and sentiment are correlated, sentiment analysis identified nuanced opinions not captured by star ratings alone.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <img src="static/images/nlp/average_ratings.png" alt="Average Ratings by Product" class="img-fluid viz-img">
